      "title": "Nevada Smith (1965) Steve McQueen · Karl Malden",
      "description": "In the western based on a novel by Harold Robbins , Steve McQueen plays the role of an avenger. Three years earlier, Alan Ladd played Nevada Smith in \" The Carpetbaggers \" Although Steve McQueen , at 36, was already a bit too old for the role, the hard-hitting Western directed by Henry Hathaway became a veritable box office hit.   The film grossed a then-astonishing five million dollars. Incidentally, the name Nevada Smith served as a model for a later screen celebrity: Indiana Jones .",
